rk\u00f6ping]]\n[[Category:Sports competitions in Bor\u00e5s]]\n[[Category:Sports competitions in \u00d6rebro]]\n", "name_user": "46.7.6.223", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(I fixed mistake)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1958_FIFA_World_Cup"}
